---
// MinecraftCard.astro
---

<div class="mc-card">
  <h2>Minecraft <span class="subtitle">简要信息</span></h2>
  <ul class="info-list">
    <li><span>☆</span> 8+ 年游玩经验</li>
    <li class="tcs-item"><span>☆</span> 主要活跃于 <a href="https://tcscraft.com" target="_blank">TCS服务器</a></li>
  </ul>
  <div class="mc-tags">
    <div class="item">
      <a href="https://namemc.com/profile/HaiHome.1" target="_blank">
        <img src="/namemc.svg" alt="NameMC" />
        <span>HaiHome</span>
        <span class="arrow">→</span>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="item">
      <a href="https://namemc.com/profile/Importser.1" target="_blank">
        <img src="/namemc.svg" alt="NameMC" />
        <span>Importser</span>
        <span class="arrow">→</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .mc-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 24px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    width: 100%;
  }

  h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--text-primary); margin: 0; }
  .subtitle { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-secondary); font-weight: normal; }
  
  .info-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }
  
  .info-list li { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
  .info-list li span { color: #facc15; }

  .info-list a {
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .info-list a:hover {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .mc-tags {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  .item {
    height: 48px;
    background: var(--bg-page);
    border-radius: calc(var(--radius) / 2);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .item a {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 0 16px;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    transition: background 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .item a:hover {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }
  
  .item img {
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    display: block;
    object-fit: contain;
    filter: invert(8%) sepia(18%) saturate(1637%) hue-rotate(185deg) brightness(91%) contrast(97%);
  }

  .arrow {
    margin-left: auto;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }
</style>